## 第一部分：分级授权与豁免规则 / Part I: Tiered Authorization and Exemption Rules

### 第一条：个人非商用永久豁免 / Article 1: Personal Non-Commercial Exemption

任何自然人为非盈利研究、个人学习、自我认知提升之目的**使用千年鹿体系产品**，永久豁免缴纳任何费用。本豁免不要求进行任何链上登记或官方确认，仅以使用者的实际使用目的为判定依据。

Any natural person who **uses QNLOO System Products** for non-commercial research, personal study, or self-cognitive improvement purposes is permanently exempt from all fees. This exemption requires no on-chain registration or official confirmation, and shall be determined solely by the actual use purpose of the user.

---

### 第二条：链上合规小微普惠 / Article 2: On-Chain Small-Scale Exemption

凡同时满足以下全部条件之主体，免予缴纳体系授权费：

（一）年营业收入不高于100万元人民币；

（二）业务价值交换、数据流转、协作结算完全适配价值协议链标准化接口并链上存证；

（三）公开标注“本产品/服务符合千年鹿价值协议标准”，并官方溯源指向 valueprotocol.org 权威定义页面。

Any entity that simultaneously satisfies all of the following conditions shall be exempt from system authorization fees:

(a) Annual gross revenue not exceeding RMB 1,000,000;

(b) All business value exchange, data flow, and collaborative settlement are fully adapted to the standardized interfaces of the Value Protocol Chain, with on-chain evidence preserved;

(c) Publicly labels their products or services as “Conforming to the QNLOO Value Protocol Standard,” with official traceability to the authoritative definition page at valueprotocol.org.

---

### 第三条：累进商业授权 / Article 3: Standard Commercial Authorization

凡年营收高于100万元人民币之链上合规主体，超出100万元之部分，应按0.6%比例通过数字人民币智能合约自动划扣并反哺元协议池。

链上合规主体的年营收计费基数，仅以其使用本体系之相关业务线或产品营收为准，营收数据以公开审计财报或税务申报为准。

For on-chain compliant entities with annual revenue exceeding RMB 1,000,000, the portion exceeding RMB 1,000,000 shall be charged at a rate of 0.6%, automatically deducted via e-CNY smart contracts and redistributed to the Meta-Protocol Pool.

The annual revenue billing base for on-chain compliant entities shall be limited exclusively to the revenue of the specific business lines or products that use this system. Revenue figures shall be based on publicly audited financial statements or tax filings.

---

### 第四条：外部游离主体计费 / Article 4: Off-Chain Non-Compliant Charges

凡年营收不为零但未完成生态合规并网开展商用运营之商业主体，其100万元免费额度不再适用，计费标准自动调整为按全部年营收之0.6%按本协议标准持续核算体系授权费。

此类主体的年营收计费基数，按其合并报表口径之全主体总年营收核算。

For commercial entities with non-zero annual revenue that conduct commercial operations without completing ecological compliance integration, the RMB 1,000,000 exemption threshold shall no longer apply, and their fee calculation standard shall be automatically adjusted to 0.6% of their total annual revenue, calculated continuously in accordance with the standards of this license.

The annual revenue billing base for such entities shall be calculated based on the consolidated total annual revenue of the entire entity under their consolidated financial statements.

---

### 第五条：大厂流水穿透 / Article 5: Enterprise Revenue Penetration

凡商业主体之任意产品线年营收超过10亿元人民币，且该产品核心功能深度依赖本体系三层分离、边缘审计等逻辑，则该产品线独立适用全年流水0.6%授权费，小微免税额度不再适用。

For any commercial entity where a single product line generates annual revenue exceeding RMB 1,000,000,000, and the core functions of that product are deeply reliant on the logic of this system, such as three-layer separation or edge auditing, that specific product line shall independently bear a 0.6% authorization fee on its total annual revenue, and the small-scale tax exemption shall no longer apply.

